{
  "text": "In the case of using 5-methylresorcinol, it was shown that a much shorter preparation time as well as a stiffer structure due to the additional directing methyl group were advantageous compared to the use of resorcinol [CITATION_1] . It was demonstrated that an industrial mixture of phenols -Honeyol \u00ae can be successfully used for obtaining aerogels [CITATION_2] . These carbon aerogels have high porosity (over 50%) and high surface areas (400-1000 m 2 g -1 ) which can be increased by a simple activation after pyrolysis as it is investigated in this research.",
  "citation_candidates": [
